    "description": "Are you a skilled Senior Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? Aptech South Asia Partners in Vadodara offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Aptech South Asia Partners:\nAptech South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aptech South Asia Partners!",
